W_{12}=W_{21}=\min\left\{ \frac{\text{share in}_{\text{1\ensuremath{\leftarrow}2}}+\text{share out}_{\text{1\ensuremath{\rightarrow}2}}}{2},\frac{\text{share in}_{\text{2\ensuremath{\leftarrow}1}}+\text{share out}_{\text{2\ensuremath{\rightarrow}1}}}{2}\right\} 
