Finds 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

 
\emph on
non-overlapping 
\emph default
communities to maximize:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Q=\sum_{c=1}^{N}\left[W_{cc}-\left(\sum_{j}W_{cj}\right)^{2}\right],
\]

\end_inset

where 
\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\xout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none

\begin_inset Formula $W_{cj}$
\end_inset


\family default
\series default
\shape default
\size default
\emph default
\bar default
\strikeout default
\xout default
\uuline default
\uwave default
\noun default
\color inherit
 is the weight edges that have one end in community 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 and the other in community 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

.
